productReviews.reviewText: I tried to nab it but got salad all over it.
I tried to behead it but got truffle all over it.
The box this comes in is 3 light-year by 5 meter and weights 10 ounce!
It only works when I'm Finland.
This Ergonomic Granite Gloves works very well. It harmonically improves my tennis by a lot.
